  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <l>R Regard not worldly wealth,</l>
   <l>I In Christ repose thy trust,</l>
   <l>C Consider well thy finall end,</l>
   <l>H How thou art but dust.</l>
   <l>A Aske mercy for thy sinne,</l>
   <l>R Reioyce in vertues lore,</l>
   <l>D Detract no time for to atchieue</l>
   <l>B Beatitudes in store,</l>
   <l>A Aboue where Christ doth raigne</l>
   <l>K King of imperiall power,</l>
   <l>E Eche Angell his triumphant praise</l>
   <l>R Resounding euery hower.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>T. T.</signed>
   </closer>
